text: Robert Karśnicki (born 20 May 1972) is a Polish former cyclist. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Poland Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Łódź
